          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5645967-laurel?shelf=read-em-once-then-it-s-done">read-em-once-then-it-s-done</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5645967-laurel?shelf=um-what">um-what</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5645967-laurel?shelf=ya">ya</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5645967-laurel?shelf=the-hell-was-this">the-hell-was-this</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5645967-laurel?shelf=who-let-you-be-heroine">who-let-you-be-heroine</a>, 
