      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/10695325-halo">Quotes from Halo</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;A man in love can do extraordinary things, I don’t care if you’re an angel, you’re my angel, and I won’t let you go.&rdquo;</span>
